Package camzup.core

Class Bounds3

java.lang.Object
camzup.core.Bounds3
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Comparable<Bounds3>
public class Bounds3
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Bounds3>
An axis aligned bounding box (AABB) for a 3D volume, represented with a minimum and maximum coordinate.
